OL,3,CNine in hospital after police and
OL,4,Cambulances called to primary school
OL,6,FNine people have been taken to
OL,7,Fhospital after emergency services were
OL,8,Fcalled to a primary school in
OL,9,FNottinghamshire.
OL,11,FPolice cars and ambulances arrived at
OL,12,FJesse Gray Primary School in West
OL,13,FBridgford after receiving a call at
OL,14,Faround 2:15pm on Wednesday.
OL,16,FPolice initially reported two pupils
OL,17,Fhad been taken to hospital, East
OL,18,FMidlands Ambulance Service (EMAS) has
OL,19,Fnow confirmed nine patients were
OL,20,Ftransported to the Queen's Medical
OL,21,FCentre.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
