OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1780646725
OL,3,CNine in hospital after police and
OL,4,Cambulances called to primary school
OL,6,FITV News Central understands all nine
OL,7,Fwere pupils at the school.
OL,9,F"The caller reported a medical
OL,10,Femergency. We sent a number of
OL,11,Fresources including paramedics in
OL,12,Fambulance cars, crewed ambulances and
OL,13,Four hazardous area response team," a
OL,14,Fspokesperson said.
OL,16,F"A responder from the air ambulance
OL,17,Fwas also in attendance. Nine patients
OL,18,Fwere transported to Queen's Medical
OL,19,FCentre."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
