OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1780646725
OL,3,CNine in hospital after police and
OL,4,Cambulances called to primary school
OL,6,FCouncillor Jonathan Wheeler, who
OL,7,Frepresents West Bridgford South at the
OL,8,Fcounty council, said he had been
OL,9,Fcontacted by residents who were
OL,10,F"concerned after spotting a large
OL,11,Fnumber of ambulances outside Jesse
OL,12,FGray School".
OL,14,FHe said he was aware of pupils who had
OL,15,Fgone to hospital for "precautionary
OL,16,Fchecks", adding: "The parents are
OL,17,Faware and I won't say more for their
OL,18,Fprivacy."
